"This algorithm detects invalid polygon geometries (self-intersections). "
"To ensure these invalid features are not filtered out before processing, "
"open |options|:sup:`Advanced options` next to the :guilabel:`Input layer`"
" and set :guilabel:`Invalid feature filtering` to ``Do not Filter (Better"
" Performance)``."
